    <item>
      <title>Effective search effort</title>
      <link>/docs/extirpation/single_cells/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/docs/extirpation/single_cells/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;pageinfo pageinfo-primary&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The IUCN defines a taxon as ‘presumed extinct’ “when &lt;em&gt;exhaustive surveys&lt;/em&gt; in known and/or expected habitat &amp;hellip;&#xA;have failed to record an individual.”&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-constitutes-a-complete-search&#34;&gt;What constitutes a complete search?&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#what-constitutes-a-complete-search&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Imagine yourself in a \(30×30m\) area (better yet, get out into the field to think this through!)&#xA;How much time do you think you need to adequately search this area?&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;There are many factors to consider here, including the size of the target organism, the complexity of its environment,&#xA;search conditions, the surveyor&amp;rsquo;s efficacy, &lt;em&gt;etc&lt;/em&gt;..&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pooling search effort</title>
      <link>/docs/extirpation/region/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/docs/extirpation/region/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Having arrived at individual values for the beta parameters for each&#xA;cell in a region (historical or potential), we then transfer these&#xA;into beta parameters for a regional distribution using moment matching:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-R&#34; data-lang=&#34;R&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#8f5902;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;# Compute beta parameters given moments&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#8f5902;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;# Taken from https://stats.stackexchange.com/a/12239&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;beta_params_from_moments&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#204a87;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;mu&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;alpha&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;((&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0000cf;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;mu&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0000cf;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;mu&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;mu&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;^&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0000cf;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;beta&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;alpha&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0000cf;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;mu&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0000cf;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#204a87;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000&#34;&gt;params&lt;